          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-10-28 12:01:51" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>to try to learn the nature or character of someone or something by submitting such to thorough and extensive testing</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to test</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to examine</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to put to the test</Gloss>
                <Gloss>examination</Gloss>
                <Gloss>testing</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It is also possible to understand {L:πειράζω&lt;SDBG:πειράζω:000000&gt;} and ἐκπειράζω in {S:04001600100014} and {S:04201002500012} as meaning ‘to try to trap’ (see {D:27.31}). See also {D:88.308}.</Comments>
