          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-10-28 12:01:51" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>to endeavor or attempt to cause someone to sin</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to tempt</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to trap</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to lead into temptation</Gloss>
                <Gloss>temptation</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It is also possible to understand {L:ἐκπειράζω&lt;SDBG:ἐκπειράζω:000000&gt;} in {S:04201002500012} as merely a process of testing (see {D:27.46}) or of trying to trap (see {D:27.31}).</Comments>
